<plot>Cantata for the King is a weird and wonderfully entertaining performance special- a post modern musical celebrating the music and genius of the King of Rock and Roll. It is a film of homage, wit, irreverent fun, and sheer sonic power. The core strength of Cantata for the King is the avant garde musical invention of John Korsrud's Hard Rubber Orchestra and the performance talents of a stellar roster of special guest soloists.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?093131</url></doc>
